data.description: OFFERING 1% lender credit when using Sellers preferred Lender, an additional 5k from seller to contribute to buyers closing cost   Step into modern comfort! This spacious home has a grand open floor plan, complemented by a cutting-edge surround system for unparalleled entertainment. Effortlessly transition with all appliances included, ensuring an stress-free move. Discover endless recreation possibilities in the huge upstairs game room with an additional half bath, perfect for entertaining your guests. It is situated near Sea World and major freeways; this home seamlessly combines practicality with modern living. Rest easy with the built in security system and be even more comfortable with a water softener already installed. Did I mention a three stage water filter and a very energy efficient home with radiant barriers and a newer water heater. Landscape is effortlessly maintained by the automated sprinkler system. Come make this house, your HOME!!
